{"sections":{"banner":{"type":"banner-image","settings":{}},"917bbf2b-cba3-4666-8e43-0a2ed853a808":{"type":"accordion","blocks":{"template--14485296676944__917bbf2b-cba3-4666-8e43-0a2ed853a808-168020443963831405-0":{"type":"panel","settings":{"heading":"OUR CANCELLATION POLICY","content":"<p>If you would like to cancel your order, please email <\/p><p><a href=\"mailto:orders@shoplittledesignco.com\">orders@shoplittledesignco.com <\/a><\/p><p>within 24 hours of placing your order. We do not accept cancellations after this 24 hour period.<\/p>"}},"template--14485296676944__917bbf2b-cba3-4666-8e43-0a2ed853a808-168020443963831405-1":{"type":"panel","settings":{"heading":"OUR EXCHANGE POLICY","content":"<p>Exchanges are always welcome within 5 days of receipt. If you choose to exchange a product, item(s) must be returned in their original packaging, otherwise we will be unable to accept the exchange.<\/p><p> <\/p><p>To exchange please send an email to <\/p><p><a href=\"mailto:returns@shoplittledesignco.com\">returns@shoplittledesignco.com<\/a> <\/p><p>and include the following information:<\/p><p> <\/p><p>Reason for exchange<\/p><p>Order number<\/p><p>Date ordered<\/p><p>Date received<\/p><p>Items you would like to exchange for<\/p><p> <\/p><p> <\/p><p><strong>Important Notes:<\/strong><\/p><p> <\/p><p>• Please note that Little Design Co. is not responsible to pay for return shipping arrangements.<\/p><p>• Exchange merchandise must be in new condition, and subject to inspection by Little Design Co.<\/p><p>• We have the right to refuse a return\/exchange in situations deemed necessary.<\/p><p>• Please note that your order can only be processed for an exchange one time. Once you have received your exchange items they are non-returnable.<\/p><p>• Colors may vary from how they appear on your screen. We highly recommend ordering a sample prior to purchasing to avoid exchanges and potential restocking fees.<\/p><p>• If your order is at all customized, no exchanges or returns will be accepted under any circumstances. For example : custom size , custom detail, etc.<\/p>"}},"template--14485296676944__917bbf2b-cba3-4666-8e43-0a2ed853a808-168020443963831405-2":{"type":"panel","settings":{"heading":"OUR RETURN POLICY","content":"<p>All items, are made to order, as fabric is on hand. Therefore, items are non-returnable unless there is a defect. Please contact us if there is a problem with any product that you receive within 2-3 days of receipt. If you are returning, item(s) MUST be returned in its original packaging, otherwise you will not be refunded.<\/p><p>In order to return an item please send an email to <\/p><p><a href=\"mailto:returns@shoplittledesignco.com\">returns@shoplittledesignco.com <\/a><\/p><p>and include the following information :<\/p><p>Order number<br\/>Date ordered<br\/>Date received<br\/>Image of defect<br\/>Reason for return<\/p><p><strong>Important Notes:<\/strong><\/p><p>• All products that leave our studio undergo a detailed quality control inspection and are approved for shipping.<\/p><p>• If your order is at all customized, no exchanges or returns will be accepted under any circumstances. For example : custom size , custom detail, etc.<\/p>"}},"59bf27ff-2b08-4dba-a4c2-b97a309f5120":{"type":"panel","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"Heading","content":"<p>Use this text to share information about your brand with your customers. Describe a product, share announcements, or welcome customers to your store.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--14485296676944__917bbf2b-cba3-4666-8e43-0a2ed853a808-168020443963831405-0","template--14485296676944__917bbf2b-cba3-4666-8e43-0a2ed853a808-168020443963831405-1","template--14485296676944__917bbf2b-cba3-4666-8e43-0a2ed853a808-168020443963831405-2","59bf27ff-2b08-4dba-a4c2-b97a309f5120"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"","allow_multiple":true,"reduced_width":true,"section_padding":"both"}},"breadcrumbs":{"type":"breadcrumbs","disabled":true,"settings":{}},"16801952994a583547":